  <name>Ro-Start</name>
  <summary>Modern welcome application for Linux distributions</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="tr">Linux dağıtımları için modern karşılama uygulaması</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Ro-Start is a next-generation welcome application that replaces traditional 
      welcome screens with a modern "Liquid Glass" aesthetic. It combines the 
      system-level power of Python with the reactive UI capabilities of React.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Beautiful visualization of CPU, GPU, RAM, and Storage statistics</li>
      <li>System update management with package manager integration</li>
      <li>Driver installation and management</li>
      <li>Software recommendations</li>
      <li>Autostart configuration</li>
      <li>Multi-language support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
